=Bio=

" I am a technology strategiest and researcher. I spent the past decade working for 4 large open source companies Red Hat, Suse, Sun Microsystems and Terrasoft (yellow dog linux) in roles that involved hands on technical competence and strategy at mid and senior management levels. 

I am basically from India and spent large parts of the last decade in Sweden and Norway. 

In the past couple of years I have authored various papers on open source, platforms and governing the commons a list of my publications can be found here :http://www.cristin.no/as/WebObjects/cristin.woa/wa/fres?sort=ar&la=en&action=sok&pnr=472

